E2Y.F.summary: EEMS Italia SpA operates in the semiconductor and photovoltaic sectors. It offers assembling and testing services for semiconductor and DRAM memories; and engineering, development, and installation services for turnkey photovoltaic systems. The company is based in Cittaducale, Italy.
